Optical Profilers
Photonics SpectraAug 2010Veeco Instruments Inc.Request Info 
        

Veeco Instruments Inc. has unveiled the ContourGT Surface Metrology
product family, its 10th generation of noncontact, 3-D optical surface profilers.
Based on proprietary white-light interferometry technology, the devices feature
patented higher brightness and dual-LED illumination. They produce fast angstrom-to-millimeter
vertical resolution over large fields of view, with flexible sample setup and good
repeatability to enable precision measurements, even in difficult applications.
Featuring 64-bit multi-core computer operation with the company’s Vision64
operating and analysis software, and an intuitive, modular user interface, the profilers
are designed to increase yield and decrease manufacturing costs. They are suitable
for use in production quality assurance/control and R&D machining and manufacturing
applications within the high-brightness LED, solar, ophthalmic, semiconductor, medical
device and academic research markets.Visit company websitehttp://www.veeco.comAbout this supplier/Company.aspx?CompanyID=15663



